{"tid":2268823,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"社評：選情逆轉 特朗普勝算在握！","createTime":"2020-11-03T05:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T12:39:14.000Z","uid":66087,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd26a3a1fddc0ba1810fab06705d15f69a5ab93","tid":2268823,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"11月3日 社評<br />\n<br />\n美國總統大選於當地時間3日正式投票。今次選情激烈，期間更爆出拜登家族醜聞。主流民調一直指向拜登領先，到最近才出現特朗普領先；2020年總統「選舉人團」的選情地圖統計分析顯示，特朗普將以322比216大勝拜登。從種種跡象顯示，特朗普勝算在握。<br />\n<br />\n在美國大選前最後一個周末，特朗普和民主黨總統候選人拜登在選戰重地集會拉票，作最後衝刺。兩位候選人均強調投票者面對的決定性選擇；拜登攻擊特朗普對疫情的處理，特朗普則警告拜登若當選，將斷送美國的未來。<br />\n<br />\n美國賭博網站Oddschecker於11月2日的消息顯示，66%的賭博人士認為，2020美國總統大選中特朗普將打敗拜登。<br />\n<br />\n全球最大網上博彩公司「必發」（Betfair Exchange）發言人休斯（Darren Hughes）說，截至10月28日上午，該公司已收到下注額2.2億英鎊（約22億港元）。即使不計算其後注碼的數額，已超過4年前特朗普對希拉里的總統大選的1.99億英鎊（約19.9億港元）的下注紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n這場具足爭議性的總統選舉走勢可以說是峰迴路轉，在拜登家族醜聞出現後，兩大科技巨頭、社交媒體平台Facebook及Twitter曾一度屏蔽消息，甚至封鎖爆料《紐約郵報》的帳號。不過，此舉卻為該兩間公司帶來經濟損失，反映市場普遍意見。"},{"pid":"92dd67772fc2418812a79b2217d5de2d12c5dce5","tid":2268823,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"侵侵民調逆轉，賠率又贏，今次冇得輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fbc91ebee015a152b026a634891608edd0f900","tid":2268823,"uid":177168,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0FQ6Ru.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0FQ6Ru.png&h=487b53e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9021a685e105d795dbe6b0cf410721e44c3a009f","tid":2268823,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"Mark Taylor: trump 會連任<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2268737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2268737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c0c3714b66b76bbd2473830e4d58a4ad4a119be","tid":2268823,"uid":71213,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxzqVLz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxzqVLz.gif&h=3ca1c6c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccf1122b25b0bbffd72b188b24684ed8b740a975","tid":2268823,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"False news <br />\n沉睡💤拜登必勝<br />\n<br />\n（習帝成最大贏家）"},{"pid":"8087fca20fad505bdc240f939dde64dda1c915b3","tid":2268823,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"大比數贏呀"},{"pid":"1830d0d99e4d534e76cc47042f918b3dc3b1cc97","tid":2268823,"uid":47775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"我登必勝呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342953d5bbcdb59c1e1a55c254fdc28d0f6e4907","tid":2268823,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"我燈勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbb545e6f16336ee4fd473fcff07b5eb717a5df","tid":2268823,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"但拜登先係熱門 解釋吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d25c3f9e0b5ac405336329745f38e7445c36460","tid":2268823,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"92dd67772fc2418812a79b2217d5de2d12c5dce5","tid":2268823,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"侵侵民調逆轉，賠率又贏，今次冇得輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:39:14.000Z","msg":"真係冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}